<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;">JD Intelligent Customer Service Full-link Solution</p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;">The launch of JD's intelligent customer service training robot conduces to less pressure for customer service training teachers in each industry, save costs of personnel management and enhances training efficiency; In addition, as it supports different types of business training, it improves businesses and skills of customer service, and largely increases customer satisfaction.</p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p>
<p style="text-indent: 2em;">In the future, with the continuous development of AI technology, the understanding ability of intelligent customer service robots will become stronger and the learning and interaction ability will also be greatly improved. Thus, more problems of human customer service will be handled. JD Cloud & AI will constantly provide each industry with full-stack AI capability and offer more efficient, convenient solutions based on its full-scenario, full-process product matrix, so as to support the construction of a safer, more flexible and more advanced intelligent customer service training system, and realize more social value.</p>
